<h1>La Guardia Civil busca a Puigdemont en un aeródromo de Barcelona</h1>
    




    





    
    
    
    

    <time class="op-published" datetime="2018-01-24T10:01:55Z">January 24, 2018 10:01:55 AM</time>
    <time class="op-modified" dateTime="2018-01-24T11:09:51Z">January 24, 2018 11:09:51 AM</time>

    






    
    
        
    

















    
        
            
        
        
        
    

    
        

        
            
        
    

    
        
    

    
        
    






<figure>
    <img src="https://www.economiadigital.es/uploads/s1/53/19/35/1/636448098018344099_15_970x597.jpeg" />

    
        <figcaption>La Guardia Civil est&aacute; vigilante ante un posible regreso de Puigdemont. EFE</figcaption>
    
